  - import.meta.filename => string absolute path with symlinks resolved (file: => path form)
  - import.meta.dirname => directory name string (path dirname of import.meta.filename)
  - import.meta.main => boolean true when module is process entrypoint (stability noted v24+)
  - import.meta.resolve(specifier) => returns string absolute URL that specifier would resolve to; signature: import.meta.resolve(specifier: string) -> string
- Dynamic import expression:
  - import(specifier) is asynchronous and returns a Promise resolving to the module namespace object; can load both ESM and CommonJS interop forms
